    "In this context, marketers can leverage scent to create emotional connections with consumers, enhancing product recall and loyalty.",
    "In contrast, gustatory signals are detected by taste buds on the tongue, responding primarily to soluble substances.",
    "These signals are relayed through cranial nerves to the brain, which identifies basic tastes-sweet, sour, salty, bitter, and umami.",
